{"tid":2012490,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話山卡啦唔好：大埔嵐山風涼水冷 （AA無飯開）","createTime":"2020-05-11T16:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T21:01:59.000Z","uid":89349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"099bbdfcb14b1d4dc03be7361043ad64f804081e","tid":2012490,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20140721/large/1405931489_a464.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n長實（001）新盤大埔嵐山1期，自上周推出價單以及屋苑內有巨墳，長實執行董事趙國雄今早到電台解畫，否認為「賺到盡」推出超細單位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他表示：項目每平方呎售價只是7000元至8000元，貼近現時興建新樓盤的「成本價」，「唔係賺到盡，係平，單價（呎價）又平，總價都平。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他指出，賣2萬元一呎，才算是「賺到盡」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於樓盤出現最細177呎單位，他否認是「劏房」格局，「我哋最細嘅單位177呎都唔係好細，如果劏房有咁大，咁住緊劏房嘅市民會好高興。」趙國雄指出，「已經是四五年前入則，無考慮到（今日）劏房流行。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62de2c5983f65ef459ffd64e8812522f02441422","tid":2012490,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/7v6mJNQ.gif\" />"},{"pid":"7603308410ada3146e9227c608144acaaa32e0e7","tid":2012490,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"62de